description: AMUNDI S&P 500 UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the S&P 500 Index (total return index), whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to the 500 largest stocks on the US market, with a single transaction. The S&P 500 is recognised as the leading benchmark index of the US market. For further information on index rules, please refer to the fund prospectus or eu.spindices.com.
name: Amundi S&P 500 UCITS ETF - USD (C)
